description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/4516/documentation

Rough estimation based on use of materials and information for construction works by one company. Life time 30 years.;[This dataset was already contained in the ecoinvent database version 2. It was not individually updated during the transfer to ecoinvent version 3. Life Cycle Impact Assessment results may still have changed, as they are affected by changes in the supply chain, i.e. in other datasets. This dataset was generated following the ecoinvent quality guidelines for version 2. It may have been subject to central changes described in the ecoinvent version 3 change report (http://www.ecoinvent.org/database/ecoinvent-version-3/reports-of-changes/), and the results of the central updates were reviewed extensively. The changes added e.g. consistent water flows and other information throughout the database. The documentation of this dataset can be found in the ecoinvent reports of version 2, which are still available via the ecoinvent website. The change report linked above covers all central changes that were made during the conversion process.]

Materials, land use, energy use of construction company and dismantling of pipelines.

processDocumentation.timeDescription: Data for materials published in 1980. Environmental data for construction of pipelines in 2000.
processDocumentation.dataTreatmentDescription: From single data to global situation.
processDocumentation.samplingDescription: Literature and environmental report of a multinational company.
